Package: cssem
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Fitted Construct-State Structural Equation Modeling
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person(
    "Hohjin",
    "Im",
    email = "hohjini@uci.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
)
Description: Research implementation of the measurement foundation for CS-SEM.
    It estimates theory-declared manifestation constructs with scale-aware,
    cross-fitted construct states and reports recovery, stability, and
    measurement diagnostics. Structural and causal modeling are intentionally
    outside version 0.1.
